Comment: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:33.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Comment: 0,0:23:01.81,0:23:06.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:08.36,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Once there was a man who obtained everything,\Nthe legendary Pirate King Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:12.86,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,His last words before he was executed inspired people to sail the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:14.63,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,All my wealth and treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:16.27,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,It can be yours if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:17.42,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,Search for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.42,0:00:19.79,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything in that one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:22.82,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,People now set sail in search of romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:25.40,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The world has entered a Great Age of Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:37.18,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,All pirates who seek One Piece\Nstrive to reach the second half of the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:39.76,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The place called the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:45.00,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,And now, the boy who ate the Gomu Gomu Fruit\Nand became a rubber man,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:48.14,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nare going to challenge that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.15,0:02:52.57,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:03:00.95,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,In order to reach their next stage, the New World, the Straw Hat Pirates have gone to Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:06.45,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,There they find that the New Fishman Pirates\Nare planning to overthrow the Ryuuguu Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:09.93,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The crew find themselves drawn into local events.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:13.96,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Friend or foe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:14.97,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,You guys can...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:19.33,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,decide that for yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:40.53,Main,Citizen,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who broke into Navy HQ twice two years ago... Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:43.36,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,They even brought their ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:45.74,Main,Pirate2,0000,0000,0000,,It's the entire Straw Hat crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:17.21,Main,Daruma,0000,0000,0000,,Who would've thought that Straw Hat was hiding inside the shark's mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:22.37,Main,Zeo,0000,0000,0000,,But didn't we leave that skeleton tied up in Ryuuguu Palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:24.97,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,We were waiting for you, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:25.91,Main,Fishman2,0000,0000,0000,,They actually came!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:30.62,Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Madame Shyarly,\Nthe pirate with the hat just showed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:32.46,Main,Kid2,0000,0000,0000,,He saved the Royal Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.61,0:04:35.28,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:42.38,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Was that good enough, Jinbe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:45.43,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,For Luffy, don't you think he did pretty good?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:50.35,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but things didn't exactly go according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:52.89,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:55.39,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,I will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:58.31,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-chin... Boss Jinbe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:00.86,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we just gonna stand around?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:04.45,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, excuse me, my father's life is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:06.60,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I said move, so move already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:09.70,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to kick their asses,\Neven if I have to go through you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:13.31,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,How many times are you going to make me say it?\NI told you to wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:14.79,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to what I have to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:18.08,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of relationship do we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:18.96,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:20.79,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:27.11,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,For years now, it's been a struggle for fishmen and humans to create a simple relationship like ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:30.50,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,The reason why I told you not to fight with Hody...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.50,0:05:35.04,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,is because I didn't want you to start a reckless fight.\NDon't act rashly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:44.24,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,If you just beat up Hody, then the people of this island will see you as nothing but another heartless human.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:45.99,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:50.12,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,please become the hero who saved Fishman Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:53.70,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:54.58,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:55.54,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:05:57.70,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,We're pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:06:01.21,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I love heroes, but I don't wanna be one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:06.17,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even know what it means to be a hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:07.14,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:09.37,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, think about the meat, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:11.95,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates eat meat at huge feasts,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:15.02,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,but heroes have to take the meat and share it with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:17.02,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna eat the meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:20.33,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of logic is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:23.02,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,He's just worried about meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:27.69,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.  I'll give you meat, so just do what I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.69,0:06:28.49,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:30.57,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,It's that easy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:34.82,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,To put it simply, I'll have you help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:36.95,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you can do that, it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:37.75,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:43.82,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, first Megalo and I will\Nintentionally get captured and infiltrate their position.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:49.63,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,And then, when I have their attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:54.73,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,one of you will stealthily\Nsneak out of Megalo's stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:56.61,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,From inside his stomach?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:04.86,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,And then you'll get the Celestial Dragons' form.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.65,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What form?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:14.07,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, Luffy was asleep,\Nso he barely heard a word of Jinbe's story.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:23.46,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's a very important piece of paper that\NQueen Otohime risked her life to get ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:27.80,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,The other thing we need is\Nthe key to the King's chains.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:32.30,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Stealing those things...\NDo we have someone who can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:37.10,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the theft to me.\NI could do it... with Robin's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.18,Main,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,Quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:44.15,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,So after you've freed the King, I'll ask Luffy-kun to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:49.53,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,And then you'll make a grand entrance out of Megalo's stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:53.99,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone will understand that\NLuffy-kun and I are working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:08:01.25,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,The Princess can wait in a safe location\Noutside the plaza, ready to take the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:04.42,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Then she can escape with the King and the others,\Nonce they have been freed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:10.71,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,While that is happening, the rest of you\Nwill hurry to Ryuuguu Palace and release our allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:14.73,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Once that's done, hurry back to the plaza.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:18.39,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,As for how you free our allies in the palace...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.34,0:08:21.85,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Come up with something yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:23.81,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.33,Main,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,Super-leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.33,0:08:31.94,Main,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,I've got the Sunny,\Nso I'll be sure to come up with that something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:38.01,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,If we follow this plan,\Nhow do you think the citizens will react?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:38.78,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,You two?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:47.25,Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Jinbe-san is respected by both the citizens of the island and the villagers from the Fishman District.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:53.22,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, if everyone sees that Boss trusts Luffy-chin with his life while they save the King,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:56.47,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,then I'm sure that everyone will cheer for Luffy-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:08:58.89,Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:01.35,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:07.18,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only doing it because\Nyou're the one who's asking, Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:11.15,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Being cheered on by everyone will just distract me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:14.28,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't happen very often, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:19.66,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,With mermaid ladies cheering for me, I could defeat the devil himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:21.04,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.95,Main,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, it appears to be settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:26.72,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:32.09,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still worried about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:33.55,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,What should we name this operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:35.58,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need a bloody name!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:37.39,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:43.81,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like they were able\Nto rescue our allies from Ryuuguu Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:45.06,Main,Papagg,0000,0000,0000,,Straw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:47.67,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Pappagg!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:49.69,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're not hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:50.65,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,But, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:54.08,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,I kept thinking I was about to die because of these guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:59.56,Main,Citizen,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}Straw Hat Luffy is a human pirate that's on our side, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:03.05,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Shirahoshi asked him for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:07.86,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,He's come with Boss Jinbe to save this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:09.33,Main,Fishmen,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:13.36,Main,Zeo,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like you've become quite popular...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:16.30,Main,Zeo,0000,0000,0000,,but you shouldn't get cocky\Njust because you snatched the King away from us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:20.40,Main,Zeo,0000,0000,0000,,You're still just human pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.40,0:10:23.78,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Mermaid Princess-san, you are so lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:29.81,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but you wouldn't let me see your panties, would{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:32.23,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,Cut that out!  She's the Mermaid Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:34.00,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, can I settle for Nami-san's?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:35.23,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,Settle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:41.07,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it looks like everyone's finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:42.49,Main,Daruma,0000,0000,0000,,They totally ignored you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:46.29,Main,Zeo,0000,0000,0000,,I said it quietly intentionally so they couldn't hear me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:51.86,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-swan!  I was the one who saved those idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:52.87,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Have you fallen for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.87,0:10:53.79,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:58.24,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot, we made it to the exit by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:10:58.92,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:03.05,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I saved you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:04.81,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,Pappagg, you saved them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:08.35,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, Brook became a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:09.69,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:14.65,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.  I was able to make good use of a new technique that I've learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:23.45,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,We're in a hurry, you see. \NSo if you'd get those keys... no wait, those swords?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:25.26,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,You see, time's running out...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:27.78,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from me, Ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:32.24,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Pappagg-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:42.05,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Why does a ghost know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:45.04,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.  Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.66,0:11:49.77,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Wha!  I don't know any ghosts!  Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:52.98,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't happen to be... Bones?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:07.55,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Th-th-the water's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:12.19,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Brook?!  We're running out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.88,0:12:14.86,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:16.10,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:20.51,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:33.10,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Marvelous, Zoro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:35.84,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Great, Zoro!  We're free!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:56.06,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,You're cutting way too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:12:57.04,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:01.69,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,I can't swim any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:03.56,Thoughts,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold my breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.56,0:13:04.33,Thoughts,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:06.86,Thoughts,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:12.64,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro, Usopp, Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:15.10,Main,Frankie,0000,0000,0000,,We super-came to greet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:16.79,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we made it just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:20.01,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:23.84,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,Brook's new technique sounds amazing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:24.82,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,but even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:33.54,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,They don't look worried at all,\Neven though Luffy took out their captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:35.83,Main,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.  How strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:57.89,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.65,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,The Celestial Dragons' form.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:04.42,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, every one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:08.99,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,This is Fishman Island's greatest hope,\Nit's my mother's legacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:12.37,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,But then again, Weak-hoshi is bit of a liability.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:17.35,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly wasn't part of my plan\Nfor her to be captured,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:18.87,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm not sure how to get her out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:23.34,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama, are you talking about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:23.95,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.45,0:14:27.76,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Just that, up until now you've been calling me, "Wimp."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:32.68,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I didn't know all the details.\NYou're not as much of a wimp as I thought you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:35.30,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,So from now on, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:37.29,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Weak-hoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:45.01,Main,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,Anybody can react with anger and hatred\Nwhen they are faced with trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:49.30,Main,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that man who was insulting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.67,0:14:58.33,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,A wimp would never have the strength\Nto hold all of that hatred inside of themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:15:00.37,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:04.21,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been incredibly trying\Nfor Princess Shirahoshi over all those years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:10.84,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,My sincerest apologies.  This is all happening\Nbecause I kept the truth to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:14.57,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.  You should be proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:20.31,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,We mustn't let the hatred get the better of us.\NThose great people wouldn't want us to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:24.40,Flashbacks,Tiger,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,900)}Don't tell the people on our island anything! { from 543 }
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:31.86,Flashbacks,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}Don't lose yourself in anger and hatred because of me. { from 546 }
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:36.66,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,You planted a small seed in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:39.15,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,We can hope that the seed\Nwill grow and cover the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.15,0:15:43.09,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,If a day comes when\Neveryone thinks the same way as you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.09,0:15:45.68,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,then there would be no more strife between fishmen and humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:49.63,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,and the cycle of revenge would disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.02,0:15:54.70,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to disrespect those long years that you endured...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:16:02.61,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Alone day after day,\Nprotecting that seed with your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:06.52,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,But now, we'd like your permission to help protect that seed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:27.96,Main,Shiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:34.78,Main,Shiroshi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:40.77,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a wimp, but you sure are a crybaby!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:45.27,Main,Fishmen,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!  Go get 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:51.17,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Vander Decken wasn't of any use at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:54.95,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,He was supposed to eliminate Shirahoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:56.32,Main,Pirates,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:57.87,Main,Zeo,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:17:01.33,Main,Zeo,0000,0000,0000,,The Energy Steroids are still in his system.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:04.96,Main,Daruma,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he took so many!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:07.04,Main,Daruma,0000,0000,0000,,The captain's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:22.90,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary Mermaid Princess with her troubling power...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:27.36,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,All he had to do was eliminate Shirahoshi quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.36,0:17:31.32,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Hell, and now I've been played for a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:38.14,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Jinbe... I should have figured it out\Nwhen you let yourself be captured so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:44.37,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,You've really become a human-lover!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:48.79,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,You're the type of person I hate the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:54.85,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Fisher Tiger and your sworn brother Arlong\Nwere both raised in the Fishman District with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:58.09,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,and both of them were killed by humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:18:02.90,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,But instead of avenging your brother's death, you've gone and made friends with the one who killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:07.26,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,You've become even worse than Neptune,\Nyou damned coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:11.55,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,When I become the king of this island,\Neverything will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:16.28,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,This year's World Council Meeting will be the perfect opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:21.81,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to Mariejoa and slaughter\Nall the human kings of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:26.11,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Then the curtain will rise on\Nour feared undersea kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.49,0:18:34.18,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,We'll drag all the humans of the world\Ndown to the sea floor, and make them our slaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:38.44,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually there will be no one left\Nto oppose fishmankind!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.44,0:18:40.34,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,It will be the same in the world of piracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.54,0:18:48.77,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,All of the pirates will grovel\Nin front of the New Fishman Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:50.60,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:54.95,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,These are the faces of the pirates who know my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:18:58.76,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,This is your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:04.49,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat, in the end I will be the one\Nworthy of being called Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:07.93,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate King?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:15.96,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,What can a mere ten pirates do?\NA mere breath from me is enough to send you flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:18.28,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,I've got one hundred thousand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:28.39,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,How does Straw Hat and Boss Jinbe stand a chance against that many with only ten people?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:33.10,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,If they lose this fight,\Nthen Hody will take Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:37.65,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to flee\Nfrom the only homes we've ever known.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:40.78,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Win!  Straw Hat!  Boss Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:42.16,Main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:45.16,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them, New Fishman Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:49.69,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,There's one hundred thousand of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.69,0:19:52.09,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,How can we fight that many?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.09,0:19:53.42,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:57.09,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing good has ever come\Nfrom being friends with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:20:01.48,Main,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we may be crushed\Nbefore we even get a chance to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:03.30,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Crushed!?  Too scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:05.59,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,So, one hundred thousand enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.59,0:20:09.45,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly is an astonishing amount.\NIt's enough to make your eyes pop out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:12.98,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,But then, I don't have any eyes to pop out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:17.32,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,What's one hundred thousand enemies?!  Let's get it started!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:21.65,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Easy for you to say!\NYou're using us as human shields!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:25.69,Main,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,So my time has finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:29.91,Main,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,Super Armored Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:32.79,Main,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come at me from wherever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:38.73,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,We have ten people...\Nso each of us have to take out ten thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:42.24,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Superior numbers doesn't always mean strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:46.68,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like they're Navy elites or anything.  You're cowering for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:50.26,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Who's cowering, you shitty moss-head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.26,0:20:53.23,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,You are, you little nosebleed chef!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:57.81,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:20:59.61,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,L-Luffy-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:01.56,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:05.44,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take his 400 million head!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.44,0:21:06.84,Main,Pirate2,0000,0000,0000,,No, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:08.62,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'll let you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:11.45,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:49.82,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:09.89,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,He took out a hell of a lot of pirates without even lifting a finger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:12.06,Main,Pirate2,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  Pull yourselves together!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.49,0:22:15.56,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!  He dropped half of us in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:19.56,Main,Pirate2,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty thousand.... just like that?!  What the hell did he do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.05,0:22:21.86,Main,Citizen,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.86,0:22:23.98,Main,Citizen2,0000,0000,0000,,What?  What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.98,0:22:26.69,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,You can really do it, can't you, Straw Hat Boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.59,0:22:29.98,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hat pirate did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.98,0:22:31.66,Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.01,0:22:33.46,Main,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,Was that haki?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.46,0:22:36.25,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,He has come so far in just two years?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:40.60,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,The Color of the Conqueror.  He had it all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.60,0:22:44.50,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,If he wasn't at least this strong,\Nthen I'd have to become the new captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.50,0:22:46.97,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Luffy-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.48,0:22:51.22,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,You're Hody, right?  I have to kick your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.04,0:22:56.10,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna go around and become the king of\Nsome countries, then that's none of my business...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.83,0:23:01.81,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,But there's only room for one Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.86,0:23:12.20,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The showdown between the New Fishman Pirates and the Straw Hat Pirates has begun at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.20,0:23:18.00,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The crew have to protect Shirahoshi while they are surrounded by fifty thousand pirates led by Hody.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.55,0:23:25.67,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro and Sanji finally reveal the new techniques that they learned during their intensive two year training.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.67,0:23:27.21,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on One Piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.21,0:23:28.80,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,An Explosion of Skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:30.34,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro and Sanji Begin Their Assaults!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:32.76,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
